IAAC -  iNFRA as a Code 


Automation of infra creation ..


AZURE -  Terraform , Ansible , Poweshell , ARM (Azure resource Manage Templates)

AWS. - Terraform , Ansible , Powershell , Cloud formation templates


=============

How to run terraform code ..

1) Terraform init >> this will initilise the terraform version 

2) Terraform plan >> This will generate the plan ( it will tell you whta are the resources going to create)

3) Terraform Apply >> This will create the resources 

====
4) Terraform destroy >> this will delete all the resources created using terraform scripts.